CatDescriptText: A number of newspapers are lying on the desk in image. One masthead reads: "Cleveland Edition, Pittsburgh Courier" with headlines reading, "Christmas for Nixons Will B. . .", "Racketeers Planning Open Gang War?" and " 'No Compromise - President Truman' ".  A wreath in the left corner of Courier reads, "Courier Xmas Story".
TitMainTitle: Men, including P. L. Prattis on right, and Mal Goode in background, and women, including Jessie Vann, in Pittsburgh Courier offices, with Christmas tree in back room
